        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/index.html" class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1a3a3a] tracking-tight">골든타임 라운지</a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm font-medium">
                <a href="/deposit/index.html" class="hover:text-[#c5a059] transition">제2의 월급</a>
                <a href="/tax/index.html" class="hover:text-[#c5a059] transition">절세와 상속</a>
                <a href="/health/index.html" class="hover:text-[#c5a059] transition">취업과 건강</a>
